      "writtenOn": "2019-05-14T03:26:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I remembered more about this issue. There\u0027s currently no mechanism to propagate various env vars needed for gsutil/git/docker/etc. auth to indirect consumers of \"system\" account. So even if kitchen sets up all necessary proxies, our hypothetical upload_to_gs script won\u0027t know how to contact them.\n\nSo this change is fine, it doesn\u0027t remove any capabilities (since they didn\u0027t exist).",
